<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1696] Deprecate old &lt;highlighting&gt; syntax and move configuration to HighlightComponent</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1696</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is no reason why we should have a custom syntax for highlighter configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It can be treated like any other SearchComponent and all the configuration can go in there.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12444580">SOLR-1696</key>
            <summary>Deprecate old &lt;highlighting&gt; syntax and move configuration to HighlightComponent</summary>
